        {
            "title": "川普警告可能對伊朗發電廠和橋樑發動攻擊",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ae3OCk7O4eJ3aGUyWhp_pA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_3_M_1440048334.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 美國總統川普週四晚間在Truth Social上發文警告,可能進一步升級對伊朗的軍事行動,稱包括橋樑和發電廠在內的關鍵基礎設施可能成為攻擊目標。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普表示:「我們的軍隊……甚至還沒有開始摧毀伊朗剩下的設施。接下來是橋樑,然後是發電廠。」他補充說,德黑蘭的新領導層「知道必須做什麼……而且要快。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這番言論標誌著美國在最近對伊朗基礎設施(包括一座主要橋樑)發動攻擊後,言辭出現急劇升級,並預示著可能對關鍵設施展開更廣泛的攻擊。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3c14c594-10b2-3e9e-bcd7-db1ab6e896e9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普發表此番評論之際,該地區緊張局勢加劇,華盛頓此前曾威脅,如果伊朗不滿足包括重新開放荷莫茲海峽在內的地緣政治要求,將以該國能源網路為攻擊目標。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普總統在週四的演講中誓言,將在未來幾週「極其猛烈地」打擊伊朗,同時也暗示軍事目標「即將完成」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最新聲明也顯示,美國正轉向加強施壓,以促成快速的政治變革。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">針對發電廠等民用基礎設施的攻擊可能會大幅擴大衝突範圍,並擾亂區域能源供應,引發對全球經濟影響的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%B0%8D%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E7%99%BC%E9%9B%BB%E5%BB%A0%E5%92%8C%E6%A9%8B%E6%A8%91%E7%99%BC%E5%8B%95%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-044748269.html",
